ResMonsterDisplayDesc.Desc_SCN: 矮人步兵是人族的初级地面单位。虽然单兵作战能力不如兽人战士，但矮人步兵性价比高、可以量产。
ResMonsterDisplayDesc.Desc_EN: Dwarf Infantry is the primary ground unit for the Humans. Although combat effectiveness is not as great as Orc Warriors, they are cost-effective and can be mass produced.

ResMonsterDisplayDesc.Desc_SCN: 这些出色的射手，拥有强大的远程输出能力，并能承担起对付敌方空军的任务。
ResMonsterDisplayDesc.Desc_EN: These outstanding marksman have powerful ranged attacks. They can also fight against aerial enemies.

ResMonsterDisplayDesc.Desc_SCN: 咒术师是强大的魔法单位。减速魔法可以让被施法单位丧失部分战斗力，变形术可以让某个单位完全丧失战斗力。
ResMonsterDisplayDesc.Desc_EN: Conjurers are powerful magic wielders. They can lower enemies effectiveness through their slow magic. Morph can make a unit completely lose its combat power.

ResMonsterDisplayDesc.Desc_SCN: 修女可以帮助你恢复那些受损单位的生命并有驱散的能力，同时圣盾术还可以提升部队的战斗力。
ResMonsterDisplayDesc.Desc_EN: Clerics can help recover health of damaged units and have the ability to disperse. Divine Shield can also improve combat effectiveness of the troops.

ResMonsterDisplayDesc.Desc_SCN: 飞行的攻城单位，可以给建筑带来相当大的伤害。但高攻击力的代价就是射程很近，且只能攻击地面。
ResMonsterDisplayDesc.Desc_EN: Flying Siege units can do great damage to buildings. But the price of high attacks means they must be close to their target and ground attack only.

ResMonsterDisplayDesc.Desc_SCN: 他们是魔法力量的守卫者，他们身披抗魔盔甲以免受到魔法的攻击，同时拥有法术迁移的能力。只能攻击地面。
ResMonsterDisplayDesc.Desc_EN: These are the guardians of magic. They are wearing anti-magic armor which stops magic attacks. They also use Spell Transfer.

ResMonsterDisplayDesc.Desc_SCN: 若论单挑能力，没有任何空军兵种可以战胜鹰骑士，因为从战斗开始的那一刻，对方就会被鹰骑士牢牢锁住，无法动弹。
ResMonsterDisplayDesc.Desc_EN: If you are short handed then no Aerial units can defeat the Eagle Rider. Once the battle begins your opponent will be locked down and unable to move.

ResMonsterDisplayDesc.Desc_SCN: 重装骑士是人族的高级地面兵种，拥有超高的机动能力，冲锋能让他们在战斗开始时迅速给予敌人打击。
ResMonsterDisplayDesc.Desc_EN: Heavy Knight is a high level Human troop. They have high mobility and their charge allows them to quickly charge the enemy.

ResMonsterDisplayDesc.Desc_SCN: 重型装甲车，能对建筑造成毁灭性打击，被炮车的烟雾弹笼罩的敌军防御建筑，将丧失战斗力。机械单位拥有较高的魔法抗性。
ResMonsterDisplayDesc.Desc_EN: Heavy armored vehicles can cause devastating blows to buildings. Defensive buildings will be shrouded from smoke bombs and will lose their fighting power. They also have high Magic Resist.

ResMonsterDisplayDesc.Desc_SCN: 威力巨大的人族高级飞行单位，龙骑士不仅有着出色的生存能力，还有着致命的杀伤力。
ResMonsterDisplayDesc.Desc_EN: Powerful Human aerial unit. The Dragon Knight has high survivability and is also very lethal.

ResMonsterDisplayDesc.Desc_SCN: 可以升级至二级城堡，升级后可解锁中级兵种和中级科技，提升基地等级可提高基地和副基地的战斗力。保护基地不被摧毁对获得战争的胜利至关重要！
ResMonsterDisplayDesc.Desc_EN: Can be upgraded to level 2 castle, after upgrading intermediate Troops and Tech will be unlocked. It also increases combat effectiveness of base and secondary base. Protecting your base is vital to winning!

ResMonsterDisplayDesc.Desc_SCN: 兽人战士是兽族凶猛强悍的集中表现，也是兽族部落的前锋和中坚力量。
ResMonsterDisplayDesc.Desc_EN: The Orc Warrior is the essence of Orc fierceness and power. He is the backbone of the Orc tribe.

ResMonsterDisplayDesc.Desc_SCN: 当地精炮手和近战单位组合成混合部队的时候，其战斗力相当的强大。地精炮手也可以用来对抗空中单位。
ResMonsterDisplayDesc.Desc_EN: Goblin Gunners are combined with melee troops they are quite strong. Goblin Gunners can also attack aerial units.

ResMonsterDisplayDesc.Desc_SCN: 兽人术士作为强大的战场支援，可以使用电磁乱流和兽神祝福大大提升队友的输出能力，并且自身有驱散魔法的能力。
ResMonsterDisplayDesc.Desc_EN: Orc Warlocks are great at supporting your team in battle. They can use Electromagnetic Blast and Beast Blessing to increase ally ability. They can also disperse magic.

ResMonsterDisplayDesc.Desc_SCN: 萨满是兽人部队的重要组成部分，麻痹药剂的控制能力和治疗链接的恢复能力，令它在兽人的部队中有着举足轻重的地位。
ResMonsterDisplayDesc.Desc_EN: Shamans are important parts of the Orc army. They can control enemies with Paralyze poison, and they can heal with Treatment Link

ResMonsterDisplayDesc.Desc_SCN: 神秘的食人魔祭司能通过命运和空间的力量，为自己和队友减免伤害，高级祭司还能复活阵亡的兽人战将。
ResMonsterDisplayDesc.Desc_EN: The mysterious Ogre Cleric through the power of fate and space can reduce damage inflicted on self and allies. High level Ogre Clerics can also resurrect Orc Centurions.

ResMonsterDisplayDesc.Desc_SCN: 巨狼骑士主要用来对付敌方建筑,利用禁锢之环让敌方单位暂时无法移动并将空中目标拉到地面。
ResMonsterDisplayDesc.Desc_EN: The Wolf Knight is mainly used to attacking buildings. With Imprison the they can stop enemy movement and pull aerial units to the ground.

ResMonsterDisplayDesc.Desc_SCN: 轻型飞行单位，在与敌方空中单位交火时，它还可以投出威力巨大的炸弹伤害空中敌军。
ResMonsterDisplayDesc.Desc_EN: Light aerial units can hit other aerial units and also drop bombs on them as well.

ResMonsterDisplayDesc.Desc_SCN: 巨翼飞龙可以通过搭配兽神祝福来增强战斗力，在敌方的对空力量相对薄弱的时候，巨翼飞龙的攻击往往是非常致命的。
ResMonsterDisplayDesc.Desc_EN: Combat dragons match up well with Beast Blessing. When the enemies’ airpower is weak, their attack can be deadly.

ResMonsterDisplayDesc.Desc_SCN: 兽族的投石车是攻城战之中的主力，它可以投射出炎爆弹打击远处的建筑。作为机械单位，拥有较高的魔法抗性。
ResMonsterDisplayDesc.Desc_EN: The Orc Catapult can deliver devastating blows to enemy buildings by launching bombs from far away. As a mechanical unit it has high Magic Resist.

ResMonsterDisplayDesc.Desc_SCN: 强大的兽人战将以勇猛和骄傲著称,是最强大的地面战士，威力巨大的撼地一击让他们在地面战场上难寻敌手。
ResMonsterDisplayDesc.Desc_EN: The powerful Orc Centurion is known for the bravery and pride. It is the most powerful ground warrior and their rivals are few and far between.

ResMonsterDisplayDesc.Desc_SCN: 地狱犬是阵亡的怨灵聚集而成，作为亡灵最基本的作战单位，它们拥有强大的恢复能力。
ResMonsterDisplayDesc.Desc_EN: Cerberus are the embodiment of sadness and hate. A basic Undead unit they have strong resilience.

ResMonsterDisplayDesc.Desc_SCN: 巨型蚂蚁是强大的对空力量，虽然巨型蚂蚁无法攻击空中目标，但可以用唾液将空中单位拉到地面并攻击。
ResMonsterDisplayDesc.Desc_EN: Giant Ants are powerful against Aerial units. Although they cannot attack them directly they use saliva to pull them to the ground then attack them.

ResMonsterDisplayDesc.Desc_SCN: 黑暗灵媒是死不瞑目的灵魂转化而来，游走在亡灵之界。她们的降魂术能降低敌人的战斗力，还能召唤灵之暗面保护友军。
ResMonsterDisplayDesc.Desc_EN: The Dark Mystic is transformed from an unspeakable soul and wanders the realm of Undead. Their magic can reduce the enemy’s combat power and summon dark spirits to protect allies.

ResMonsterDisplayDesc.Desc_SCN: 死灵法师是灾难的代言人，这些亡灵的法师可以从墓地复活亡灵战士，并用黑暗法术提高周围友军的作战能力。
ResMonsterDisplayDesc.Desc_EN: Necromancer is a master of disaster. These masters of the Undead resurrect dead warriors from the cemetery and use dark spells to improve the combat effectiveness.

ResMonsterDisplayDesc.Desc_SCN: 噬魂鬼是亡灵族强大的战士，它们能对血肉之躯造成额外伤害，并从伤痛中汲取力量。
ResMonsterDisplayDesc.Desc_EN: Life Takers are powerful Undead warriors who cause extra damage to those of flesh and blood. They gain strength from others’ pain.

ResMonsterDisplayDesc.Desc_SCN: 这些邪恶的鬼面兽是天生的狩猎者，当敌人是空中单位时鬼面兽将发动鬼爪旋风造成范围伤害。
ResMonsterDisplayDesc.Desc_EN: Ghost Win are born hunters. When the enemy is an aerial unit, Ghost Wing will launch a ranged attack called Ghost Whirlwind.

ResMonsterDisplayDesc.Desc_SCN: 瘟疫战车除了能用炮弹为战场带去瘟疫，还能将灵魂收集起来供死灵法师召唤亡灵战士。机械单位拥有较高的魔法抗性。
ResMonsterDisplayDesc.Desc_EN: In addition to being able to bring plague upon the battlefield, the Plague Chariot can also collect souls for the Necromancer to create more Undead warriors. Mechanical units have high Magic Resist.

ResMonsterDisplayDesc.Desc_SCN: 巨锤恶魔携带着死亡之源从地狱之门降临，它携带的死气会持续侵蚀它周围的敌人直到带走他们的生命。
ResMonsterDisplayDesc.Desc_EN: Sledgehammer brings death from the gates of hell. The dead air that surrounds him will continue to harm enemies.

ResMonsterDisplayDesc.Desc_SCN: 幽暗巨兽拥有威力巨大的喷吐攻击，敌人被命中时，强大的能量紊乱使它们被减速，当目标是建筑物时将被彻底禁锢。
ResMonsterDisplayDesc.Desc_EN: Dark Behemoth has a powerful spit attack. When the enemy is hit they will be Slowed, if the target is a building then it will be Imprisoned.

ResMonsterDisplayDesc.Desc_SCN: 噬魂恶魔是从噬魂鬼蜕变而来，它们不惧怕魔法，除了拥有跟噬魂鬼相同的吸血能力还能触发狂暴大幅度增强自身战斗力。
ResMonsterDisplayDesc.Desc_EN: Soul Reaper is a product of Life Takers. They are not afraid of magic and they use the same Life Steal ability as Life Takers, they can trigger and increase their combat power through violence.

ResMonsterDisplayDesc.Desc_SCN: 精灵战士是受到了月神祝福的部队，他们能将受到的伤害反弹给攻击者本身，更能在夜晚发挥更强的力量。
ResMonsterDisplayDesc.Desc_EN: The Elf Warrior is blessed by the Moon God. They can ricochet attacks back to attackers and have more power at night.

ResMonsterDisplayDesc.Desc_SCN: 射手是精灵部队的第一梯队，敏捷的身手可以让他们在一瞬间射出两根箭矢伤害多个敌人。
ResMonsterDisplayDesc.Desc_EN: This archer is an ancient class of Elf. Their quick and agile skills allow them to shoot 2 arrows at once to hit multiple enemies.

ResMonsterDisplayDesc.Desc_SCN: 驭风女巫是自然之力的代言人，他们使用自然之咒去弱化他们的敌人，经验老道的女巫还能召唤飓风来摧毁敌人的战斗力。
ResMonsterDisplayDesc.Desc_EN: Storm Witches are representatives of Nature. They use Nature Curse to weaken their enemies. Experienced Storm Witches can even summon Hurricanes.

ResMonsterDisplayDesc.Desc_SCN: 魔力幽龙是在魔法滋养下成长的生物，他们能灵敏的躲避即将到来的伤害，在感应到附近的魔力流动时，它们能迅速的作出反击。
ResMonsterDisplayDesc.Desc_EN: The Rune Dragon feeds on Magic. They can avoid damage and when they sense the flow of magic they can quickly counterattack.

ResMonsterDisplayDesc.Desc_SCN: 狂野兽灵常年在丛林中磨练出了野性的本能，他们能运用自然之力治疗受伤的友军，更能变身成凶猛的狂狮去摧毁敌人。
ResMonsterDisplayDesc.Desc_EN: Wild Elf, from years in the jungle has true wild instincts. They can use the power of Nature to treat ally injuries and can morph into a fierce lion.

ResMonsterDisplayDesc.Desc_SCN: 成群的鹰身兽无疑是敌方空军的噩梦，他们的普攻能在敌方空军之间弹射。
ResMonsterDisplayDesc.Desc_EN: Gryphon’s are a nightmare to aerial units. They are like a catapult against aerial units.

ResMonsterDisplayDesc.Desc_SCN: 对魔法的亲和让森林魔女不会受到任何魔法的伤害，同时她们能清除任何对友方不利的魔法效果。
ResMonsterDisplayDesc.Desc_EN: Their closeness to Magic allow the Forest Witch to have immunity against Magic attacks. Also they can remove Magic de-buffs on friendly troops.

ResMonsterDisplayDesc.Desc_SCN: 远古兵器的强力一击可以穿透目标，对目标身后的敌方也造成伤害。
ResMonsterDisplayDesc.Desc_EN: The Ancient Weapon can penetrate through the target and damage the target behind it.

ResMonsterDisplayDesc.Desc_SCN: 巨大的树人能给敌方造成巨大的压力，逼迫周围的敌人去攻击他。同时，树人身上还会生成爆裂果实伤害周围的敌人。
ResMonsterDisplayDesc.Desc_EN: Giant Trees can put lots of pressure on the enemy forces to attack them. They will also damage troops around them with their Bursting Fruit.

ResMonsterDisplayDesc.Desc_SCN: 双头龙是来自空中的梦魇，它的两个头颅分别掌控着闪电与剧毒的力量，它对建筑喷吐的毒液是所有建筑的噩梦。
ResMonsterDisplayDesc.Desc_EN: Double-Headed Dragon, is truly a force from the air. The two heads control lightning and poison and the venom spit on buildings is extremely destructive.

ResMonsterDisplayDesc.Desc_SCN: 矮人步兵是人族的初级地面单位。虽然单兵作战能力不如兽人战士，但矮人步兵性价比高、可以量产。
ResMonsterDisplayDesc.Desc_EN: Dwarf Infantry is the primary ground unit for the Humans. Although combat effectiveness is not as great as Orc Warriors, they are cost-effective and can be mass produced.

ResMonsterDisplayDesc.Desc_SCN: 这些出色的射手，拥有强大的远程输出能力，并能承担起对付敌方空军的任务。
ResMonsterDisplayDesc.Desc_EN: These outstanding marksman have powerful ranged attacks. They can also fight against aerial enemies.

ResMonsterDisplayDesc.Desc_SCN: 咒术师是强大的魔法单位。减速魔法可以让被施法单位丧失部分战斗力，冰封术可以让某个单位完全丧失战斗力。
ResMonsterDisplayDesc.Desc_EN: Conjurers are powerful magic wielders. They can lower enemies effectiveness through their slow magic. Morph can make a unit completely lose its combat power.

ResMonsterDisplayDesc.Desc_SCN: 修女是人族部队的重要组成部分，可以帮助你恢复那些受损单位的生命，同时圣盾术还可以提升部队的战斗力。
ResMonsterDisplayDesc.Desc_EN: Clerics can help recover health of damaged units and have the ability to disperse. Divine Shield can also improve combat effectiveness of the troops.

ResMonsterDisplayDesc.Desc_SCN: 飞行的攻城单位，可以给建筑带来相当大的伤害。但高攻击力的代价就是射程很近，且只能攻击地面。
ResMonsterDisplayDesc.Desc_EN: Flying Siege units can do great damage to buildings. But the price of high attacks means they must be close to their target and ground attack only.

ResMonsterDisplayDesc.Desc_SCN: 他们是魔法力量的守卫者，他们身披抗魔盔甲以免受到魔法的攻击，同时拥有法术迁移的能力，对使用魔法的敌方兵种是一个巨大威胁。只能攻击地面。
ResMonsterDisplayDesc.Desc_EN: These are the guardians of magic. They are wearing anti-magic armor which stops magic attacks. They also use Spell Transfer.

ResMonsterDisplayDesc.Desc_SCN: 若论单挑能力，没有任何空军兵种可以战胜鹰骑士，因为从战斗开始的那一刻，对方就会被鹰骑士牢牢锁住，无法动弹。
ResMonsterDisplayDesc.Desc_EN: If you are short handed then no Aerial units can defeat the Eagle Rider. Once the battle begins your opponent will be locked down and unable to move.

ResMonsterDisplayDesc.Desc_SCN: 重装骑士是人族的高级地面兵种，拥有超高的机动能力，冲锋能让他们在战斗开始时迅速给予敌人打击。
ResMonsterDisplayDesc.Desc_EN: Heavy Knight is a high level Human troop. They have high mobility and their charge allows them to quickly charge the enemy.

ResMonsterDisplayDesc.Desc_SCN: 重型装甲车，能对建筑造成毁灭性打击，被炮车的烟雾弹笼罩着的敌军防御建筑，将丧失战斗力。作为机械单位，拥有较高的魔法抗性。
ResMonsterDisplayDesc.Desc_EN: Heavy armored vehicles can cause devastating blows to buildings. Defensive buildings will be shrouded from smoke bombs and will lose their fighting power. They also have high Magic Resist.

ResMonsterDisplayDesc.Desc_SCN: 威力巨大的人族高级飞行单位，龙骑士不仅有着出色的生存能力，还有着致命的杀伤力。
ResMonsterDisplayDesc.Desc_EN: Powerful Human aerial unit. The Dragon Knight has high survivability and is also very lethal.

ResMonsterDisplayDesc.Desc_SCN: 兽人战士是兽族凶猛强悍的集中表现，也是兽族部落的前锋和中坚力量。
ResMonsterDisplayDesc.Desc_EN: The Orc Warrior is the essence of Orc fierceness and power. He is the backbone of the Orc tribe.

ResMonsterDisplayDesc.Desc_SCN: 当地精炮手和近战单位组合成混合部队的时候，其战斗力相当的强大。地精炮手也可以用来对抗空中单位。
ResMonsterDisplayDesc.Desc_EN: Goblin Gunners are combined with melee troops they are quite strong. Goblin Gunners can also attack aerial units.

ResMonsterDisplayDesc.Desc_SCN: 兽人术士作为强大的战场支援，可以使用电磁乱流和兽神祝福大大提升队友的输出能力。
ResMonsterDisplayDesc.Desc_EN: Orc Warlocks are great at supporting your team in battle. They can use Electromagnetic Blast and Beast Blessing to increase ally ability. They can also disperse magic.

ResMonsterDisplayDesc.Desc_SCN: 萨满是兽人部队的重要组成部分，麻痹药剂的控制能力和治疗链接的恢复能力，令它在兽人的部队中有着举足轻重的地位。
ResMonsterDisplayDesc.Desc_EN: Shamans are important parts of the Orc army. They can control enemies with Paralyze poison, and they can heal with Treatment Link

ResMonsterDisplayDesc.Desc_SCN: 神秘的食人魔祭司能通过命运和空间的力量，为自己和队友减免伤害，高级祭司还能复活阵亡的兽人战将。
ResMonsterDisplayDesc.Desc_EN: The mysterious Ogre Cleric through the power of fate and space can reduce damage inflicted on self and allies. High level Ogre Clerics can also resurrect Orc Centurions.

ResMonsterDisplayDesc.Desc_SCN: 巨狼骑士主要用来对付敌方建筑,利用禁锢之环让敌方单位暂时无法移动并将空中目标拉到地面。
ResMonsterDisplayDesc.Desc_EN: The Wolf Knight is mainly used to attacking buildings. With Imprison the they can stop enemy movement and pull aerial units to the ground.

ResMonsterDisplayDesc.Desc_SCN: 轻型飞行单位，在与敌方空中单位交火时，它还可以投出威力巨大的炸弹伤害空中敌军。
ResMonsterDisplayDesc.Desc_EN: Light aerial units can hit other aerial units and also drop bombs on them as well.

ResMonsterDisplayDesc.Desc_SCN: 巨翼飞龙可以通过搭配兽神祝福来增强战斗力，在敌方的对空力量相对薄弱的时候，巨翼飞龙的攻击往往是非常致命的。
ResMonsterDisplayDesc.Desc_EN: Combat dragons match up well with Beast Blessing. When the enemies’ airpower is weak, their attack can be deadly.

ResMonsterDisplayDesc.Desc_SCN: 兽族的投石车是攻城战之中的主力，它可以投射出炎爆弹打击远处的建筑。进攻敌人基地的时候，带上投石车。作为机械单位，拥有较高的魔法抗性。
ResMonsterDisplayDesc.Desc_EN: The Orc Catapult can deliver devastating blows to enemy buildings by launching bombs from far away. As a mechanical unit it has high Magic Resist.

ResMonsterDisplayDesc.Desc_SCN: 强大的兽人战将以勇猛和骄傲著称,是最强大的地面战士，威力巨大的撼地一击让他们在地面战场上难寻敌手。
ResMonsterDisplayDesc.Desc_EN: The powerful Orc Centurion is known for the bravery and pride. It is the most powerful ground warrior and their rivals are few and far between.

ResMonsterDisplayDesc.Desc_SCN: 射手是精灵部队的第一梯队，敏捷的身手可以让他们在一瞬间射出两根箭矢伤害多个敌人。
ResMonsterDisplayDesc.Desc_EN: This archer is an ancient class of Elf. Their quick and agile skills allow them to shoot 2 arrows at once to hit multiple enemies.

ResMonsterDisplayDesc.Desc_SCN: 兽人战士是兽族凶猛强悍的集中表现，也是兽族部落的前锋和中坚力量。
ResMonsterDisplayDesc.Desc_EN: The Orc Warrior is the essence of Orc fierceness and power. He is the backbone of the Orc tribe.

ResMonsterDisplayDesc.Desc_EN: Goblin Gunners are combined with melee troops they are quite strong. Goblin Gunners can also attack aerial units.

ResMonsterDisplayDesc.Desc_EN: These outstanding marksman have powerful ranged attacks. They can also fight against aerial enemies.

ResMonsterDisplayDesc.Desc_SCN: 地狱犬是阵亡的怨灵聚集而成，作为亡灵最基本的作战单位，它们拥有强大的恢复能力。
ResMonsterDisplayDesc.Desc_EN: Cerberus are the embodiment of sadness and hate. A basic Undead unit they have strong resilience.

ResMonsterDisplayDesc.Desc_SCN: 巨型蚂蚁是强大的对空力量，虽然巨型蚂蚁无法攻击空中目标，但可以用唾液将空中单位拉到地面并攻击。
ResMonsterDisplayDesc.Desc_EN: Giant Ants are powerful against Aerial units. Although they cannot attack them directly they use saliva to pull them to the ground then attack them.
